@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kmykau(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.72 / v2) * wp.abs(0.76))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.cos(0.93)
    tmp = 0.45
    v0 = v1
    v2 = 0.85
    tmp = 0.04
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.12) - 0.81))
    data[tid] = v0
